column2: Which company offered the best package last year?
column3: Infosys has offered the best package last year through pool drive.
There is no placement calendar so far for SPMVV. You can reach out to following website for available resources: https://www.spmvv.ac.in/school-of-engineering-technology/placement-training/

column2: Can I accept the offer letter?
column3: Yes, but respond before the **deadline** mentioned in the offer.
